                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-778-18430130 t18430130-778-punishment-185"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">SPICER</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
